=Battle Through The Heaven=

18
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:29,980
=Episode 23=

19
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,440
Xuan Kong Zi.

20
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,880
So it was because...

21
00:02:39,390 --> 00:02:40,720
You must have lost your mind.

22
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:43,870
Wind Sage.

23
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,560
Who is this?

24
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:49,960
She is Xuan Yi
who died in the battle

25
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:52,830
with the Hall of Souls
fifty years ago.

26
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:55,320
Elder Xuan Yi.

27
00:03:01,670 --> 00:03:02,510
Qiu Ling.

28
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,440
Your Master isn't trying
to set you up,

29
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:05,830
he's trying to save you.

30
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,240
Did he collude
with the Hall of Souls or not?

31
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:12,160
It is precisely because of his collusion
with the Hall of Souls

32
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:13,920
that he is trying to frame you

33
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:15,110
and exclude you,

34
00:03:15,170 --> 00:03:16,960
to ensure that you will not
enter the Star Region.

35
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,080
Why?

36
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:23,160
Because everyone

37
00:03:23,210 --> 00:03:24,470
who enters the Star Region dies.

38
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:25,800
Master.

39
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,990
Is there something wrong
with the Three Thousand Burning Flame?

40
00:03:28,020 --> 00:03:30,160
The problem doesn't lie
with the Three Thousand Burning Flame,

41
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:32,440
but with the formation symbols
on the magic ice coffin.

42
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:35,110
This is the evil method
of the Hall of Souls.

43
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:37,830
Your Master Xuan Kong Zi

44
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,390
must have made a deal
with the Hall of Souls

45
00:03:39,830 --> 00:03:41,080
in order to resurrect Xuan Yi.

46
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:42,990
Activating the formation

47
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,770
requires the power of Heavenly Flames
from Three Thousand Burning Flame.

48
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,910
If I'm right,

49
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:48,510
this secret room

50
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,270
must be connected to the Star Region.

51
00:03:51,270 --> 00:03:53,030
And those ten selected alchemists

52
00:03:53,830 --> 00:03:56,390
should be the bargaining chips
given to the Hall of Souls.

53
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:59,630
The Dou Qi of the best alchemists.

54
00:04:00,830 --> 00:04:02,360
And the formation
had been catalyzed.

55
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,520
Their next step is
to enter the Star Region

56
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,760
and let the Heavenly Flames
break out.

57
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:08,830
Xiao Yan and Brother Mu
will both enter the Star Region.

58
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:10,470
We have to stop them now.

59
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,760
Xuan Kong Zi, what are you doing?

60
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:20,110
Feng Xian.

61
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,320
You are right.

62
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:27,270
Activating the formation requires the power
of the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

63
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,440
And activating Three Thousand
Burning Flame requires

64
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:33,350
the Dou Qi of ten excellent alchemists.

65
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,720
You fell for Mu Gu's trick.

66
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,830
He is using your greed

67
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,480
to eradicate Xiao Yan
and take in the Heavenly Flames.

68
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,550
I never intended

69
00:04:43,550 --> 00:04:45,440
to let anyone from the Hall of Souls
leave alive.

70
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,440
Once the formation is activated,

71
00:04:48,230 --> 00:04:49,880
I will lock down the Star Region.

72
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:53,390
Those of the Hall of Souls will be devoured
by the Heavenly Flames.

73
00:04:54,510 --> 00:04:55,670
But nothing

74
00:04:56,350 --> 00:04:57,920
will be of use now.

75
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:03,040
I have the Seal of the Ancient Dragon of Taixu
to activate the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

76
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,480
I need no help from the Hall of Souls

77
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:06,270
nor

78
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:08,920
the sacrifice of those ten alchemists.

79
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:11,830
So you do have Zi Yan.

80
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,160
Right.

81
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,630
Zi Yan.

82
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,550
What did you do to her?

83
00:05:27,790 --> 00:05:29,040
I fed her an elixir.

84
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,320
Now

85
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,670
she's my ace in the hole.

86
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,550
Do you think you can
get away with it

87
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:37,730
after making a deal
with the Hall of Souls?

88
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:38,600
Feng Xian.

89
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,760
Feng Xian.

90
00:06:00,350 --> 00:06:02,320
My contract with the Hall of Souls
is over.

91
00:06:03,790 --> 00:06:05,550
They can no longer threaten me.

92
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:09,230
As long as you don't resist

93
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:12,790
the Taixuan Void Qi
for two hours,

94
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:15,920
it will open automatically.

95
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:19,950
By then,

96
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,270
Xuan Yi

97
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,670
should be back as well.

98
00:06:38,550 --> 00:06:39,510
- Xuan Kong Zi.
- Zi Yan.

99
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,040
Xuan Kong Zi.

100
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,760
It is too late.

101
00:06:49,230 --> 00:06:50,070
It is almost time.

102
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,640
There's no sign of Zi Yan anywhere.

103
00:07:02,550 --> 00:07:03,790
Where could they have hidden her?

104
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:09,230
No!

105
00:07:09,670 --> 00:07:10,510
Time is up.

106
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,940
Let's go to the Pill Tower now

107
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,040
and tell Elder Tian Lei Zi

108
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,440
about the plot of the Hall of Souls.

109
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,280
Okay.

110
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,350
It'll all settle down

111
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,880
when we get into the Star Region.

112
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,160
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

113
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:25,000
Entering the Star Region

114
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:27,720
is something countless people
dream of.

115
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:30,790
You're about to see
the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

116
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:33,040
Whoever is capable can take it.

117
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:05,110
Elder Tian Lei Zi.

118
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,880
Elder Tian Lei Zi.

119
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,160
The Hall of Souls has a conspiracy.

120
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,680
Mu Gu is going into the Star Region

121
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,790
to capture
the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

122
00:08:14,230 --> 00:08:15,070
Elder, be careful.

123
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,280
Elder, there's no time to explain.

124
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,590
I'll enter the Star Region first
to stop Mu Gu.

125
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,150
Please guard the gate for sure.

126
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,280
Watch out!

127
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:45,140
(Star Region)

128
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:02,630
Mu Gu.

129
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,080
Give me Zi Yan!

130
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:06,110
Since you're here,

131
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:09,710
use your Dou Qi
to conquer the Heavenly Flames.

132
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:14,590
Myriad Soul Heavenly Lock.

133
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:48,750
Zi Yan.

134
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:52,630
Mu Gu.

135
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:57,280
Our contract is null and void.

136
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,910
After I use the dragon seal
to collect the Heavenly Flames,

137
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,590
you will also be buried here.

138
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:38,280
The dragon seal does work.

139
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:40,360
Xuan Yi.

140
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,230
We'll meet again soon.

141
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:46,520
Do you think the contract
with the Hall of Souls

142
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,960
can be terminated at will?

143
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:57,110
From the moment the contract
was signed,

144
00:10:57,590 --> 00:10:59,230
you were a pawn
of the Hall of Souls

145
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,910
and the Three Thousand Burning Flame

146
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,470
was the possession of the Hall of Souls.

147
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:15,590
Xuan Yi.

148
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:19,000
We'll be reunited soon.

149
00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:26,430
Zi Yan.

150
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:30,030
Xiao Yan.

151
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,670
Take Zi Yan away!

152
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:36,400
We can't let Mu Gu
get the dragon seal.

153
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,320
No one can leave!

154
00:12:56,670 --> 00:12:57,510
Open the Star Region.

155
00:13:59,150 --> 00:13:59,990
Wind Sage.

156
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:02,430
Mu Gu.

157
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:03,760
You traitor!

158
00:14:10,110 --> 00:14:12,760
Three Thousand Burning Flame
totally broke out.

159
00:14:30,230 --> 00:14:33,080
The Hall of Souls can never
get the Heavenly Flames.

160
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:44,520
Heavenly Flame Triple Xuan Change.

161
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:35,990
Xiao Yan.

162
00:15:36,590 --> 00:15:37,760
Just die here.

163
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:40,640
I'll bring the news
of your death to Yao Chen.

164
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,760
The Three Thousand Burning Flame
can't be subdued.

165
00:15:55,550 --> 00:15:57,150
All of you, come with me!

166
00:16:00,670 --> 00:16:02,230
Xiao Yan, take Zi Yan with you.

167
00:16:21,110 --> 00:16:22,200
Xiao Yan! Hurry!

168
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:23,760
Hurry!

169
00:16:32,693 --> 00:16:34,875
Follow us!

170
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:38,920
Hurry!

171
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:53,680
Leave!

172
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:05,480
Master.

173
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:07,160
Where is Xiao Yan?

174
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:08,640
I'll go in and bring Xiao Yan out.

175
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:09,840
Wind Sage.

176
00:17:12,110 --> 00:17:14,280
You can't go back
into the Star Region again.

177
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:15,480
The Star Region

178
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,310
is a space torn apart
by the seniors of Pill Tower

179
00:17:17,430 --> 00:17:19,070
in order to store

180
00:17:19,070 --> 00:17:20,430
the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

181
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:23,190
Normally, it needs to be maintained
by Dou Qi.

182
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:25,880
After Xuan Yi was gone,

183
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:28,160
there was less Dou Qi.

184
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:30,920
The Heavenly Flames broke out.

185
00:17:31,040 --> 00:17:32,470
It is now on shaky ground

186
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:34,470
and can no longer be maintained.

187
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,190
What does that mean?

188
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:42,000
The high temperature
of the Three Thousand Burning Flame

189
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:43,640
would burn the Star Region
to the ground.

190
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:45,280
Anyone who goes in there

191
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:47,190
will just die.

192
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:11,520
Senior!

193
00:18:11,520 --> 00:18:12,360
Master!

194
00:18:12,370 --> 00:18:13,290
- Senior!
- Master!

195
00:18:13,830 --> 00:18:14,670
Senior!

196
00:18:14,670 --> 00:18:15,580
Master!

197
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:47,040
Could it be Xuan Yi's ice coffin?

198
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:53,430
It turns out

199
00:18:55,070 --> 00:18:56,520
that the secret passage
in the Pill Tower

200
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:58,350
had been connected

201
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:00,280
to the ice coffin and the Star Region.

202
00:19:03,470 --> 00:19:04,920
Senior Xuan Yi said

203
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:07,760
that tearing apart the Star Region

204
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:09,950
required a backup.

205
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:14,430
The Star Region stores
the Heavenly Flames.

206
00:19:15,310 --> 00:19:16,160
The backup

207
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:18,230
should be a glacier.

208
00:19:21,950 --> 00:19:23,040
I just didn't expect

209
00:19:25,190 --> 00:19:26,030
the glacier

210
00:19:28,430 --> 00:19:30,190
to come from her ice coffin.

211
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:15,710
The core
of the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

212
00:20:17,110 --> 00:20:18,560
I finally found you.

213
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:00,950
Zi Yan.

214
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,190
Thank you for the dragon seal.

215
00:21:02,710 --> 00:21:05,000
It seems you're really a descendant
of the Ancient Dragon of Taixu.

216
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:05,910
Dragon seal?

217
00:21:06,190 --> 00:21:07,030
What dragon seal?

218
00:21:07,430 --> 00:21:08,270
It is...

219
00:21:10,970 --> 00:21:11,820
Xiao Yan!

220
00:21:11,830 --> 00:21:12,880
- Xiao Yan!
- How are you?

221
00:21:22,760 --> 00:21:23,600
Xiao Yan!

222
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:25,600
Magic Poison Spot.

223
00:21:30,540 --> 00:21:31,820
(Starfall Hall)

224
00:21:38,590 --> 00:21:39,910
How come there's
a Magic Poison Spot?

225
00:21:41,830 --> 00:21:42,760
It must be Mu Gu.

226
00:21:43,070 --> 00:21:45,800
The Magic Poison Spot is an evil technique
of the Hall of Souls

227
00:21:46,470 --> 00:21:48,590
that specializes
in restraining Heavenly Flames.

228
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:51,280
It must be that Xiao Yan
had triggered the Magic Poison Spot

229
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,880
when he took in
the Three Thousand Burning Flame.

230
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:56,000
Master.

231
00:21:56,830 --> 00:21:58,910
Is there a cure
for the Magic Poison Spot?

232
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:02,880
There is no cure for it

233
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:04,640
unless the host who planted it dies.

234
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:07,040
The Poison Spot
is extremely damaging and poisonous.

235
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:08,230
If I make a move to suppress it,

236
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,800
his meridians must be damaged.

237
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:12,430
We can only control the outbreak
of the Magic Poison Spot first.

238
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:30,360
Master.

239
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:32,000
Let me try.

240
00:22:33,470 --> 00:22:34,680
Use my Woeful Poison Body

241
00:22:34,920 --> 00:22:36,520
to see if it can suck out
Xiao Yan's Magic Poison.

242
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:53,580
(The Yang Flame Ancient Altar's
supreme Yang power)

243
00:22:53,830 --> 00:22:55,350
(is greatly damaging
to the Woeful Poison Body.)

244
00:22:56,280 --> 00:22:58,110
(Finish it within the hour)

245
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:00,430
(or you yourself will be in danger.)

246
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:19,760
You're not yet healed. Lie down.

247
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:27,430
Little Fairy Doctor.

248
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:32,350
I didn't realize I was
the first person you healed

249
00:24:33,230 --> 00:24:35,520
after controlling
the Woeful Poison Body.

250
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:43,040
You saved yourself.

251
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:45,950
If you hadn't risked your life

252
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:48,680
to save me in Demon Flame Valley,

253
00:24:50,230 --> 00:24:53,430
there wouldn't be a Little Fairy Doctor
who could save your life today.

254
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:58,160
I used to think

255
00:24:59,280 --> 00:25:01,470
that I would end up dying
from the Woeful Poison Body.

256
00:25:03,950 --> 00:25:05,280
In your heart,

257
00:25:07,830 --> 00:25:11,000
remembering me as the Little Fairy Doctor
of Lush Town

258
00:25:13,040 --> 00:25:13,920
is enough.

259
00:25:16,830 --> 00:25:19,350
You will always be the Little Fairy Doctor
of Lush Town,

260
00:25:20,760 --> 00:25:23,280
a kind-hearted doctor.

261
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:30,430
Master.

262
00:25:31,280 --> 00:25:32,120
Wind Sage.

263
00:25:34,800 --> 00:25:35,640
Give me your hand.

264
00:25:46,520 --> 00:25:47,920
You're gifted with Heavenly Flames.

265
00:25:48,760 --> 00:25:51,270
And the Magic Poison Spot
is right at odds with Heavenly Flames.

266
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:52,280
As long as it is in your body,

267
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:54,830
you will not be able
to use Heavenly Flames.

268
00:25:55,760 --> 00:25:57,920
Little Fairy Doctor could only
temporarily seal it

269
00:25:58,040 --> 00:25:59,230
with the Woeful Poison Blood.

270
00:26:00,350 --> 00:26:01,400
Unless Mu Gu is killed,

